rows.label: qst105901_msg002
rows.name:
Oh, actually, I was thinking of
opening a shop in Superbia, but...

rows.label: qst105901_msg003
rows.name:
I lost most of my assets when
Acedia collapsed the other day...

rows.label: qst105901_msg004
rows.name:
The start-up funds I had
saved for years were
swallowed by the Cloud Sea.

rows.label: qst105901_msg007
rows.name: Ask if he can dive to retrieve it.

rows.label: qst105901_msg008
rows.name:
Yeah... But if I've had this much
bad luck, I'm hopeful that something
good will happen next.

rows.label: qst105901_msg009
rows.name:
I wish I could, but...
unfortunately, I'm not a salvager.

rows.label: qst105901_msg010
rows.name:
Besides, even if I went to
get it now, it's probably
drifted somewhere unknown.

rows.label: qst105901_msg011
rows.name:
The only thing I have on hand
that might be worth some money
is this salvaged item, but...

rows.label: qst105901_msg012
rows.name:
...it's in pretty bad shape. I doubt
even a junk shop would buy it...

rows.label: qst105901_msg014
rows.name:
...You're right. Meeting
here must be some kind of
fate. I'll leave it to you!

rows.label: qst105901_msg015
rows.name:
The junk shop is at the very end
of the Iville Commercial District,
so it should be easy to find.

rows.label: qst105901_msg016
rows.name: Sorry, but I'm counting on you.

rows.label: qst105901_msg101
rows.name: So, how'd it go? Did you sell it?

rows.label: qst105901_msg102
rows.name:
...I see. Well, it's junk, so I
guess not many people would buy it.

rows.label: qst105901_msg103
rows.name: I know it's tough, but do your best.
